perl-Gtk2-SourceView2
------------------------------------------
Perl bindings for version 2.x of the GtkSourceView library

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.0-62
  libgcc1-4.3.4-1
  libgdk_pixbuf2.0_0-2.18.3-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.22.2-1
  libgtk2.0_0-2.18.3-1
  libgtksourceview2.0_0-2.8.1-1
  perl-5.10.0-5
  perl-Glib-1.222-1
  perl-Gtk2-1.221-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.19.51-1
  cygport-0.9.10-1
  gcc4-core-4.3.4-1
  make-3.81-2
  perl-ExtUtils-Depends-0.302-1
  perl-ExtUtils-PkgConfig-1.12-1

Canonical website:
  http://search.cpan.org/dist/Gtk2-Champlain/

Canonical download:
  http://search.cpan.org/CPAN/authors/id/P/PO/POTYL/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack perl-Gtk2-SourceView2-0.04-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./perl-Gtk2-SourceView2-0.04-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/perl-Gtk2-SourceView2-0.04-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/perl-Gtk2-SourceView2-0.04-X.tar.bz2

For a list of files included in the binary package, run from the 
command-line: 'cygcheck -l perl-Gtk2-SourceView2'.

-------------------------------------------

Port Notes:

----- version 0.04-1 -----
Initial release for Cygwin 1.7.


Cygwin port maintained by:
